      * L379:              OR EMP-ANT NOT EQUAL ORD-EMP-RAZON.
      * L380:          COMPUTE AUX-TOTAL-GRAL-IMPORTE = AUX-TOTAL-GRAL-IMPORTE
      * L381:          + AUX-TOTAL-POR-EMP-IMPORTE.
      * L382:          IF LINEA-A-ESCRIBIR > 60 THEN PERFORM SALTO-DE-PAGINA.
