      * L384:          MOVE AUX-TOTAL-POR-EMP-IMPORTE TO DATO-TOTAL-POR-EMP-IMPORTE.
      * L385:          WRITE LINEA-LISTADO FROM LINEA-TOTAL-POR-EMPRESA.
